content:
A long time ago one of my managers told me &ldquo;you should write a blog!&rdquo;&hellip; I dismissed the idea back then mainly because I did not like following the trends and I did not want to make another Wordpress site on the internet&hellip;
But yesterday late night while browsing memes on 9gag I came across this picture of a Japanese girl band whose name did not come to my mind&hellip;
It bothered very much me because I remember having seen their live performance during Rockavaria festival in 2015.
While I did spend about 15 minutes on this topic I realized I tend to forget a lot of other things lately and that got me scared a little. Because of that I have decided to create such posts to remind myself of such things in the future.

These are my top. I collect them here so I can find them very quickly when I want to show them to someone &#x1f604;
